<db:titleabbrev>Qt Quick Controls 1 Reference Documentation</db:titleabbrev>
<db:abstract>
<db:para>Used to define columns in a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls-tableview.xml">TableView</db:link> or in a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls-treeview.xml">TreeView</db:link>.</db:para>
